block content
  h1= title
  p Welcome to #{title}
  p.
    dummy web-app with frontend & api (nodejs + mongoDB):
    https://medium.com/@xoor/dockerizing-a-node-js-and-mongodb-app-f9d80fdb280e
  ul 
    li POST /data/into/db:
    li $ curl -X POST -H "Content-type: application/json" http://localhost:3000/data/into/db -d '[ { "a": 1 }, { "b": 2 }, { "c": 3 } ]'
